title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update IV - Brussels
description:
In this video we will look at the city of Brussels where several POI's have been added as part of World Update IV: France/Benelux which has been released yesterday. We are using the Edgley Optica which has been released today by Aerosoar and is a free airplane which can be download via the link in the link in this description.
